        p By accessing or using Gaming Community, you agree to follow these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with these terms, please do not use the website.

      .static-section
        h2 2. About Gaming Community
        p Gaming Community is an independent online platform where users can share gaming posts, guides, reviews, tips, comments, ratings, and discussions. The platform is designed for community interaction and entertainment purposes.

      .static-section
        h2 3. User Accounts
        p Some features require an account. You are responsible for keeping your account information accurate and secure. You must not share your password, impersonate another person, or use another user’s account without permission.
        p You are responsible for all activity that happens through your account.

      .static-section
